OL,3,CInquest begins into death of girl, 5,
OL,4,Cdays after surgery
OL,6,FThe inquest into the death of a five-
OL,7,Fyear-old girl from Cornwall started
OL,8,Ftoday, Wednesday 26 November, at
OL,9,FCornwall Coroner's Court in Truro, led
OL,10,Fby the senior coroner for Cornwall,
OL,11,FAndrew Cox.
OL,13,FAmber Milnes died on the 9th of April
OL,14,F2023, four days after having a
OL,15,Fsurgical procedure to remove her
OL,16,Ftonsils and adenoids at Royal Cornwall
OL,17,FHospital.
