OL,3,CInquest begins into death of girl, 5,
OL,4,Cdays after surgery
OL,6,FThe inquest heard evidence from Dr
OL,7,FAndrew Bamber, a consultant in
OL,8,Fpaediatric pathology with North
OL,9,FBristol NHS Trust. Dr Bamber told the
OL,10,Finquest that his post mortem
OL,11,Fexamination indicated that Amber died
OL,12,Fas a result of "a severe bleed from a
OL,13,Fruptured vessel at the surgery site".
