OL,6,FThe inquest heard a pen portrait from
OL,7,FAmber's parents, Sereta and Lewis
OL,8,FMilnes, describing Amber as "our
OL,9,Fmagical little princess" who was "the
OL,10,Fgirliest of girls" who loved music and
OL,11,Fsinging. Sereta went on to describe
OL,12,Fhow Amber was "the happiest little
OL,13,Fgirl" who "is and will forever be
OL,14,Fmissed, more than words can describe".
