OL,3,CInquest begins into death of girl, 5,
OL,4,Cdays after surgery
OL,6,FA statement read out at the inquest,
OL,7,Fwritten by Amber's mother, Sereta
OL,8,FMilnes, detailed how Amber was
OL,9,Freferred to the hospital for surgery
OL,10,Fto try to alleviate her sleep apnoea
OL,11,Fand symptoms from a rare condition she
OL,12,Fhad called cyclical vomiting syndrome
OL,13,F(CVS).
OL,15,FSereta's statement said the condition
OL,16,Fcaused Amber to have prolonged
OL,17,Fepisodes of severe nausea and vomiting
OL,18,Fand that Amber could become "quickly
OL,19,Fdehydrated"; some episodes required
OL,20,Fhospital admission in the past.
