OL,3,CInquest begins into death of girl, 5,
OL,4,Cdays after surgery
OL,6,FThe inquest heard how Amber had been
OL,7,Fsent home following the surgery, on
OL,8,FApril 5 2023, with oral pain and anti-
OL,9,Fsickness medication. However, she was
OL,10,Funable to take the medicine due to the
OL,11,Fonset of CVS.
OL,13,FOn April 6 2023, Amber was readmitted
OL,14,Fto hospital and given intravenous
OL,15,Fmedication for pain relief, anti-
OL,16,Fsickness and antibiotics.
OL,18,FOn April 9, Amber died. Dr Bamber told
OL,19,Fthe inquest this was as a result of a
OL,20,F"massive haemorrhage" from a ruptured
OL,21,Fblood vessel.
