OL,6,FHe added that he did not consider the
OL,7,Fvessel to have been damaged during the
OL,8,Fsurgery but that "significant
OL,9,Finflammation and tissue damage" was
OL,10,Flikely caused by an "infection" at the
OL,11,Fsurgical site.
OL,13,FThe inquest continues.
